wiki.summary: On “Wrapped Around Your Finger”, Post Malone describes a controlling relationship he endured during a period of his life. He touches on topics like alcoholism, depression and procrastination which have culminated to a feeling of unrequited love. Letting this lover go would mean Post would lose a part of the life he holds so dearly to his heart. Unravelling himself from their finger would conclude the relationship, so he holds tight onto memories of a happier past instead of evaluating the present moment. Read more on Last.fm.
